Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory642.jpg'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Hey, Darling, wake uuuuup!', 4: '18'}
{3: 'The next morning, you once again experience the same noisy yet thoughtful "wake-up service" as yesterday.'}
{3: 'Taking a gentle sip of the "nutritious breakfast" prepared by Vie-chan, you straighten your clothes while rising from the soft mattress.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Wooow! Raven, look! Clips from last night's stream are all over the internet!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Vie-chan leans back in her gaming chair with her feet propped up on the edge of the desk, her face beaming with delight as she browses through her terminal.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: '"Vie-chan is so professional, just like a dancer!"—Hehe, you\'ve got good taste. Here\'s a like from me!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: '"So cringe, such a big streamer trying to act cute. Not as good as Meme-germ next door!"—How dare you post a comment like that! I sentence you to death!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Her expression morphs into one of irritation as she extends her tail, plugging the connector at its tip directly into the terminal.'}
{3: 'A crackling sound of electricity rises as the Goddess of the Internet delivers her impromptu judgment.'}
{2: "Isn't that a bit excessive?", 3: '25', 4: 'Good, justice is served.', 5: '25'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "How dare they run off to watch other streamers... If your loyalty to Vie-chan isn't absolute, then you're absolutely disloyal!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'From now on, everything this person posts online will be automatically replaced with "Follow Vie-chan woof, thank you for following Vie-chan woof."', 4: '1'}
{2: "...By the way, what's the theme for tonight's livestream?", 3: '30'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Hmm... it's a free chat session, so it'll mostly just be me talking.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'That reminds me, what topics should I talk about tonight?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'What about the war against adults?', 3: '35', 4: "The Supreme Leader's daily life?", 5: '37'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "No way, that's way too serious!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Ehh—no way! Even the Supreme Leader has a right to privacy!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'How about sharing your secret recipe for that love-filled breakfast?', 3: '40'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "No way, that's a special secret between me and Raven.", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Both of you fall into serious contemplation, immersed in a boundless, chaotic storm of thoughts.'}
{2: "Why don't we go out for a stroll and create some interesting topics to talk about?", 3: '45'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Hearing this suggestion, she wags her tail and displays an "Oh, I see" kind of smile.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Ohh... I get it now, so Raven wants to go on a date with me, eh?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Do you have any other suggestions?', 3: '49', 4: '...', 5: '51'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Nope, great minds think alike!', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She jumps down from the chair and takes your hand.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "I've already decided where we should go, hehe, follow me!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'The girl clutches the discount vouchers tightly in her hand as she skips forward excitedly, bouncing with each step.'}

{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory669.jpg'}
{1: 'Hyakuro Ichibancho', 2: 'Super Earth', 4: '10:30AM'}
{3: 'Super Earth, Hyakuro Ichibancho, 10:30 AM.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Ta-da! Welcome to the busiest, most prosperous commercial plaza on Super Earth.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'Vie-chan stands beneath a towering neon sign, with dazzlingly colorful streets stretching from beneath her feet all the way to the horizon.'}

{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'In the past, thousands of people would stare at the numbers here around the clock—red ones, green ones... Even the slightest change would send them into a panic, as if their lives depended on it.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'To stop everyone from obsessing over such boring things, I transformed this place into the capital of anime culture in the world!', 4: '1'}

{3: "As far as the eye can see, every building is covered with colorful billboards, electronic screens simultaneously playing clips from this season's anime, and even promotional banners for mobile games floating in the sky."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "There are some super interesting anime shops here! Let's go, let's go!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Walking with Vie-chan through crowds of people in eccentric costumes, you notice many of them casting admiring glances your way.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Eccentrically Dressed Visitor', 3: 'Whoa! Your outfit is so freaking cool! What characters are you two cosplaying? Mind sharing?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Gray Raven Commandant and the squad member.', 3: '88', 4: 'Beauty x Beast.', 5: '91', 6: 'Bodyguard and Supreme Leader.', 7: '94'}
{2: 'Gray Raven Commandant and the squad member.', 3: '88', 4: 'Beauty x Beast.', 5: '91', 6: 'Bodyguard and Supreme Leader.', 7: '94'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "That's right! I'm the Gray Raven Commandant, and Raven here is my squad member!", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Hahaha, so I'm the beaty who tames the beast?", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Dummy! Idols should keep a low profile and shouldn't casually reveal their identity, or they'll get exposed!", 4: '1'}

{3: 'Vie-chan holds your hand as the two of you stroll through the colorful streets, chatting and laughing together. In the joyful commotion, a litany of wonders rushes past, and your eyes catch only a fraction of them.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Hmm? What's that over there...", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Suddenly, a giant heart-shaped building on the side of the street catches her attention.'}
{3: "She leads you by the hand, weaving through the crowd and heading straight to the building's main entrance."}

{1: '1', 2: 'Staff Member', 3: 'Moe☆Moe☆Love! Welcome, meow.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Staff Member', 3: "Excuse meow, are you two here to experience the DokiDoki Couples' Hall? Many of our facilities require two people to enjoy together, meow know?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiFubenRpgMakerGame/FxUiFubenRpgMakerGameBubble01.prefab'}

{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiDorm/FxUiAixin.prefab', 5: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "—That's right, we heard this place is perfect for couples, so we came to check it out for ourselves.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'Before you can finish your sentence, Vie-chan suddenly cuts in.'}
{2: 'Staff Member', 3: "Ehehe, then you've come to the right place! Our establishmeownt absolutely won't disappoint any couple who visits.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Staff Member', 3: 'Our establishmeownt has prepared a gift for every couple that honors us with their presence, meow, so please accept this.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'As he speaks, he produces two wristbands from thin air.'}
{2: 'Staff Member', 3: "These wristbands are engraved with your unique ID numbers, and this small screen will display your partner's location in real-time, meow!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Ohhh—this is great! With this, Raven won't lose track of me anymore.", 4: '2'}
{3: 'She gives you a mischievous smile, her tail coiling around your bracelet and gently stroking your wrist.'}
{2: '(Puts on the bracelet)', 3: '140'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Let's go, let's go! Vie-chan's fun radar is going beep-beep!", 4: '2'}

{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory671.jpg'}
{3: 'And so, Vie-chan drags you throughout the building, racing from the ground floor to the rooftop and back down again, trying every single attraction along the way.'}
{3: 'Only when she notices your growing fatigue does Vie-chan reluctantly settle down, finding a bench where both of you can take a short break.'}
{3: "However, it isn't long before she narrows her eyes and spots a purikura photo booth nestled in the corner."}
{3: "There's no doubt that it is going to be her next victim."}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory966.png'}

{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Great, then let\'s go with the "Archangel\'s Kissy Greeting"! I love it!', 4: '1'}

{1: '1', 3: "The moment the flash goes off, an eerie sound effect plays, and Vie-chan's image on screen suddenly distorts into a jumble of corrupted code."}

{1: '1', 3: 'Turning to look at her, you find Vie-chan completely fine, grinning from ear to ear.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Splash—', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Hahahahaha! Did I make you jump? Were you scared by Vie-chan's little trick?", 4: '1'}
{3: 'She wags her tail, and the photo booth picture of the two of you on screen instantly returns to normal.'}
{1: '1005', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStoryFront/BgStoryFront30.png', 3: '0', 4: '0.1', 5: '0.4'}
{1: '1', 3: 'On the screen, Vie-chan covers her mouth, looking at the camera with a teasing smirk.'}
{3: 'Meanwhile, your startled expression has been perfectly captured and preserved.'}
{1: '1005', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStoryFront/BgStoryFront30.png', 3: '0.1', 4: '0', 5: '0.4'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "I'm keeping this photo for myself, as a special memento of today, heehee!", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "A date needs some heart-pounding moments to be truly memorable, right? Make sure you remember today's Vie-chan completely—from head to toe!", 4: '1'}
{1: 'PanelActor1Shake'}

{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "C'mon, let go! I'll take another photo with you, okay—!", 4: '1'}

{1: 'Ichiban Food Street', 2: 'Super Earth', 4: '15:00PM'}
{3: 'Super Earth, Ichiban Food Street, 3:00 PM.'}
{3: 'After several hours of play, even the ever-energetic Vie-chan finally begins to tire. She tugs at your hand and leads you to the food street outside the venue.'}
{3: 'Rich aromas from various snacks waft through the air, permeating the vibrant afternoon streets and enticing countless visitors to stop in their tracks, mouths watering.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'After all that exercise, we need to reward ourselves with something sweet! I want that crepe over there!', 4: '18'}
{1: '1', 3: 'She grabs your arm, ready to dive into the sea of people, when something seems to flash across her mind. She abruptly turns back, halting mid-step.'}
{3: 'Her eyes drop to the six or seven shopping bags dangling from your hands, an exaggerated look of embarrassment coloring her face as her lips curl into a sheepish grin.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Ehehe, I might have gotten a teensy bit carried away with shopping...', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "I'll line up by myself. What flavor would you like, Raven?", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Chocolate.', 3: '366', 4: 'Strawberry.', 5: '366', 6: "I'll have the same as you.", 7: '366'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Alright, don't wander off now. Stay put and wait for me so we can head home together, okay?", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Vie-chan turns around and weaves her way through the crowd until she reaches the queue.'}
{3: 'After she leaves, the world seems to grow a little quieter...'}
{3: 'You set down all the shopping bags of various sizes on the ground and take a moment to rest—'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory0.png'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiTheatre3/FxUiTheatre3Loading.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryWhiteNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory669.jpg'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiTheatre3/FxUiTheatre3Loading.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiDuihualiziLoopWhite.prefab', 2: '2'}
{1: '1', 3: 'Before you can enjoy this rare moment of respite, an uncanny sense of dissonance suddenly shoots through your senses.'}
{3: 'As if evading your gaze, the presence vanishes instantly into the crowd, gone in the blink of an eye.'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStory/FxUiDuihualiziLoopWhite.prefab'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineSpreadNew.prefab', 2: '2'}
{3: 'Your body moves before your mind can catch up, quickly striding toward the corner where something unusual just appeared.'}
{2: 'Assets/Product/Effect/Prefab/FxUi/FxUiStoryNew/FxUiStoryLineSpreadNew.prefab'}
{3: 'Upon reaching your destination, you scan the surroundings carefully. Everything looks perfectly normal, with no sign of anything unusual.'}
{1: '999', 2: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory669.jpg', 3: '0', 4: '1', 5: '1.5'}
{1: '1', 3: "Suddenly, that discordant splash of color appears in your vision once more, standing out starkly at the end of the street, a visual artifact you can't tear your eyes away from."}
{2: '(Chase after it)', 3: '413'}
{3: "However, it's like a mirage floating in your vision—the moment you take a step forward, it vanishes without a trace."}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/BgStory1176.jpg'}
{3: 'After a frantic pursuit, the phantom figure completely vanishes in a dim alleyway, leaving you alone and out of breath.'}
{2: 'What on earth was that thing...', 3: '420'}
{3: "You pause to catch your breath, then carefully examine the dead-end alley where that thing disappeared. There's nothing unusual to be found."}
{3: 'Soon after, the sound of leather shoes pounding on the gravel path echoes from outside the alley.'}
{3: 'The familiar girl skids to a halt before you, breathing heavily from the run.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Where did you go? I saw your position constantly changing. Do you have any idea how scared I was for you?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She glares at you with an irritated expression, holding a strawberry-topped crepe in each hand.'}
{2: 'Just now, you spotted "something" there.', 3: '433'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "What are you talking about? There's nothing here.", 4: '1'}
{2: "I can't explain it.", 3: '436', 4: 'Maybe you were seeing things...', 5: '436'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Did you play for so long that your brain started hallucinating from hunger?', 4: '1'}
{3: 'She puffs her cheeks, then without waiting for a response, forcefully stuffs a crepe into your mouth.'}
{3: 'The sweet vanilla cream, fragrant pancake, and sharp strawberry flavors abruptly fill your mouth, overwhelming your taste buds—'}
{3: 'Seeing your uncomfortable expression, Vie-chan breaks into a smug little smile.'}
{3: "Seeing that you're actually enjoying it, she stuffs your mouth with even more enthusiasm."}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Admit you were wrong? If so, just nod. From now on, no matter what happens, you're not allowed to leave me behind and run off on your own.", 4: '1'}
{3: "Just as you're about to shake your head, her tail firmly wraps around your chin, forcing you to nod against your will."}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Mmm, good job. Contract effective, validity period: lifetime.', 4: '1'}
{3: 'After delivering her "punishment," she finally releases you and properly hands over the crepe.'}
{3: 'Afterward, she nods with exaggerated seriousness, as if trying to convey some hidden message to you.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "Psst, I've heard the Supreme Leader of Super Earth absolutely loves sweet treats.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "No matter how incredibly angry she gets, as soon as she has something sweet, she'll instantly cheer right up in a flash!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'As she speaks, her tail playfully brushes against your arm, as if urging you to take action.'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: 'Raven, you—dummy!', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Vie-chan', 3: "I'm angry now! You need to feed me sweets to make me feel better!", 4: '1'}
{3: 'Against the golden horizon, she parts her lips slightly, waiting for you to feed her the sweet treat.'}
{3: 'With the setting sun, the second day of livestream training gradually fades into the twilight.'}
